PropertyGuru Singapore mobile app:
Explore and find your perfect home with PropertyGuru Singapore, the only property and real estate app you will ever need. PropertyGuru Singapore property search mobile app gives you access to a wide range of residential properties such as HDB, condo, landed houses and commercial properties in Singapore, both for sale and for rent.

Our award-winning mobile app simplifies the property search experience, making it extremely easy to search for properties for sale and for rent in Singapore. Whether you’re looking to buy a ready-to-move-in HDB or a unit in a newly launched project, the free property search app will help you with that!

Property search has never been easier: filtering and shortlisting properties matching your criteria, mapping nearby properties and providing all the essentials (photos, detailed information about the home, local neighbourhood information like MRT station, and of course agent details).

You can also easily shortlist preferred properties, contact the agent directly, or even share details of the properties with your friends by email, SMS and other social sharing platform like Facebook, Whatsapp etc.

Key Features:
- Free-text search: Search more than 210,000 properties in Singapore by entering desired MRT stations, HDB estates and locations.
- Current location: See properties for sale and for rent near you or near the MRT station you are at
- Custom property type search: Select your type of dream home (HDB, condo, apartment and landed house)
- Custom searches: Narrow down your selections by adding price range, number of bedrooms, PSF, floor size or construction date etc.
- Save your search for later, and shortlist your favourite properties
- Stay in the know: Personalized alerts across all devices and get notified with listings meeting your criteria
- Find agents: browse our Agent Directory to find a specialist in an area or project
- Instant connect: One-click contact to connect with agents by call, email or SMS
- Discover the latest new property project launches/new homes in Singapore
- Share your favourite properties with your friends and family across all sharing platforms
- Read the latest properties news on the go
- Estimate your loans with our easy-to-use Mortgage Calculator
- Multi-device, cross-platform access: Log in with your PropertyGuru account to manage your favourite searches and properties across all your devices
- You can search not only for Residential properties, but also for commercial properties

Finding a home has never been easier. Our award-winning mobile app provides a seamless experience, offering everything you need at each stage of your journey. Already have an idea of what you're looking for? Save time by filtering available properties by price, location, distance to MRT, property type, and more.

Once you've shortlisted suitable properties, contact the representing agents directly with just a click, or share details of the properties with your friends and family via email, SMS, and other social sharing platforms like Facebook and WhatsApp.

Key Features:
- (New!) My Enquiries: Manage open enquiries for your shortlisted properties, whichever channel you contacted the agent by (phone call, SMS, WhatsApp).
- Custom search filters: Search by location, property type, price, psf price, number of bedrooms or bathrooms, floor size, tenure, build year, floor level, furnishing, and more.
- Free-text search box: Looking for something more specific? Search by entering specific keywords like 'balcony', 'corner unit' and more.
- Personalised alerts: Set up notifications for new listings that match your unique search criteria.
- Home financing resources: Utilise our mortgage repayment and affordability calculators, or reach out to a PropertyGuru Finance specialist.
- Discover new projects: Learn about the latest launches and upcoming projects and developments.
- Keep up with the market: Read property news and market insights on the go.
